# 2) USER PROFILE + ADDRESS BOOK APIs
# ============================================================

### Get my profile
GET {{api}}/account/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Update my profile
PATCH {{api}}/account/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

